title: Worst Date Wednesday: Shot for Shot Until 5am
description: Ashley calls in to tell the story of how she was the bad date.  The first thing she did was bail on the guy last minute to "see if he was really interested in her".  They set up a second date but she drank until 5am the day of and passed out missing that date too.  The ending of this story will surprise you though!
